-----------------------------------------------------------
â±ï¸ Time Complexity: O(32) = O(1)  
   - Always processes exactly 32 bits.

ğŸ’¾ Space Complexity: O(1)  
   - Uses only a few variables.
-----------------------------------------------------------
"""
